## 7. CSS実装例（主要スタイル）

```css
* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: flex-start;
  min-height: 100vh;
  background: #FAF8F5;
}

/* ルートフレーム */
.sp7-access {
  width: 375px;
  padding: 32px 10px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 32px;
  background: #FAF8F5;
}

/* ページヘッダー */
.page-header {
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 5px;
  align-items: center;
}

.page-title {
  margin: 0;
  color: #1C1C1C;
  font-size: 23px;
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: -0.5px;
}

/* セクション */
.access-section {
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 7px;
}

.section-header {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
}

.section-title {
  margin: 0;
  color: #1C1C1C;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: -0.3px;
}

