---

## 8. アイコン実装の詳細

### Lucideアイコン（SVG直接記述）

**map-pin（ピン）:**
```html
<svg width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z" fill="#1E3A5F"/>
  <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3" fill="#FAF8F5"/>
</svg>
```

**alert-circle（警告）:**
```html
<svg width="7" height="7" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="#B8860B" stroke-width="2"/>
  <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12" stroke="#B8860B" stroke-width="2"/>
  <circle cx="12" cy="16" r="1" fill="#B8860B"/>
</svg>
```

**navigation（ナビ）:**
```html
<svg width="7" height="7" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <polygon points="3,11 22,2 13,21 11,13 3,11" fill="#3D6B4F"/>
</svg>
```

**car（車）:**
```html
<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <path d="M5 17H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v10a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1" stroke="#6B6B6B" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
  <circle cx="7" cy="17" r="2" stroke="#6B6B6B" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
  <circle cx="17" cy="17" r="2" stroke="#6B6B6B" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
</svg>
```

**chevron-down（下矢印）:**
```html
<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9" stroke="#6B6B6B" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
</svg>
```

